                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d74">
                <head>No. 380.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName corresp="#p_DES1" type="from"
                            >Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName corresp="#p_HF1" type="to"
                            >Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Received Feb. 10—12.10.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-02-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 10, 1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Events foreshadowed in my telegram of January 30 imminent.</p>
                <p>King has announced to cabinet his desire to abdicate. Revolution inevitable.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DES1">SICKLES</persName>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
